ing into this sport, once I started running fast, I would get the same opportunities,\\\" Johnson said according to Mile Split.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 765, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 728, \"end\": 735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.5304926584615518, \"rank\": 0.5241955451145106, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\"}, {\"begin\": 759, \"end\": 764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Split_album\", \"score\": 0.7750423224673684, \"rank\": 0.2712512922406666, \"text\": \"Split\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Split_album\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Split_album\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this sport\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"the same opportunities\", \"from\": 703, \"to\": 725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, on the track, Johnson wore HMN ALNS, an independent Black-owned brand by Phillip Mims who said he draws from diverse inspiration like streetwear, anime and runway fashion.\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 790, \"end\": 797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"score\": 0.5304926584615518, \"rank\": 0.5241955451145106, \"text\": \"Johnson\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyndon_B._Johnson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 788}, {\"ngram\": \"HMN\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"an independent Black-owned brand\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 845}, {\"ngram\": \"Phillip Mims\", \"from\": 849, \"to\": 861}, {\"ngram\": \"diverse inspiration\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"streetwear\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 920}, {\"n